@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<main class="lp-main" id="top">
		<section class="lp-hero" aria-label="Hero">
			<div class="lp-hero-grid">
				<div class="lp-hero-copy">
					<p class="lp-eyebrow">Pet-friendly venues, made simple 🐶🐱</p>
					<h1 class="lp-title">Find the right spot for you and your best friend.</h1>
					<p class="lp-subtitle">
						Discover, add, and review pet-friendly places with amenity-first filters like water bowls 💧,
						fenced areas 🧱, shade 🌳, and off‑leash zones 🎾.
					</p>

					<div class="lp-hero-actions">
						<a class="lp-btn lp-btn-primary" href="/venues">Explore venues 🔎</a>
						<a class="lp-btn lp-btn-secondary" href="#community">Add a venue ➕</a>
					</div>

					<div class="lp-chips" aria-label="Quick filters">
						<span class="lp-chip">💧 Water bowls</span>
						<span class="lp-chip">🧱 Fenced</span>
						<span class="lp-chip">🎾 Off‑leash</span>
						<span class="lp-chip">🌳 Shade</span>
						<span class="lp-chip">🪑 Dog‑friendly seating</span>
						<span class="lp-chip">🏡 Indoors / Outdoors</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="lp-hero-media" aria-label="Pet and venue photos">
					<div class="lp-mosaic">
						<img class="lp-img lp-img-1" src="images/pets/dog7.jpg" alt="Happy dog" loading="lazy" />
						<img class="lp-img lp-img-2" src="images/venues/park1.jpg" alt="Park venue" loading="lazy" />
						<img class="lp-img lp-img-3" src="images/pets/cat2.jpg" alt="Curious cat" loading="lazy" />
						<img class="lp-img lp-img-4" src="images/venues/cafe1.jpg" alt="Cafe venue" loading="lazy" />
						<img class="lp-img lp-img-5" src="images/pets/hedgehog.jpg" alt="Hedgehog" loading="lazy" />
						<img class="lp-img lp-img-6" src="images/venues/store1.jpg" alt="Store venue" loading="lazy" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="lp-section" id="features" aria-label="Features">
			<div class="lp-section-head">
				<h2 class="lp-h2">Everything you need to pick a great spot 🗺️</h2>
				<p class="lp-lead">Focused on real pet rules and amenities—not generic listings.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="lp-cards">
				<article class="lp-card">
					<h3 class="lp-h3">Amenity-first filters 🎛️</h3>
					<p>Multi-select filters for water, fences, shade, indoor/outdoor, and more—fast on mobile.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="lp-card">
					<h3 class="lp-h3">Trustworthy details ✅</h3>
					<p>Clear rules (leashed only, size restrictions) plus photos and addresses to reduce guesswork.</p>
				</article>
				<article class="lp-card">
					<h3 class="lp-h3">Community reviews ⭐</h3>
					<p>Ratings + real notes from owners, with optional amenity confirmations (“water bowls? yes/no”).</p>
				</article>
				<article class="lp-card">
					<h3 class="lp-h3">Add venues quickly ➕</h3>
					<p>Low-friction submissions: name, location, and at least one amenity/rule indicator.</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="lp-section" id="discover" aria-label="Discover">
			<div class="lp-split">
				<div>
					<h2 class="lp-h2">Discover what’s nearby (and actually pet-friendly) 📍</h2>
					<p class="lp-lead">Browse by neighborhood, skim photos, then filter down to what matters.</p>
					<ul class="lp-list">
						<li>Quick scanning with clean cards and bold labels 👀</li>
						<li>Sort by newest, rating, popularity (and distance later) 🧭</li>
						<li>Designed for mobile-first speed ⚡</li>
					</ul>
					<a class="lp-btn lp-btn-secondary" href="/venues">Start exploring 🚀</a>
				</div>

				<div class="lp-shot" aria-label="Preview images">
					<img class="lp-shot-img" src="images/venues/hotel1.jpg" alt="Featured venue" loading="lazy" />
					<div class="lp-shot-badges" aria-hidden="true">
						<span class="lp-badge">💧 Water</span>
						<span class="lp-badge">🎾 Off‑leash</span>
						<span class="lp-badge">🌳 Shade</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="lp-section" id="community" aria-label="Community">
			<div class="lp-section-head">
				<h2 class="lp-h2">Built by pet people, for pet people 🫶</h2>
				<p class="lp-lead">Add places you love, verify amenities, and help newcomers find their go-to spots.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="lp-steps" aria-label="Key flows">
				<div class="lp-step">
					<div class="lp-step-emoji" aria-hidden="true">1️⃣</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="lp-h3">Find a venue</h3>
						<p>Search by name or area, then filter by amenities and pet rules.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="lp-step">
					<div class="lp-step-emoji" aria-hidden="true">2️⃣</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="lp-h3">Check details</h3>
						<p>Photos, rules, and structured amenities help you decide quickly.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="lp-step">
					<div class="lp-step-emoji" aria-hidden="true">3️⃣</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="lp-h3">Leave a review</h3>
						<p>Rate your experience and add notes that help the next owner.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="lp-testimonials" aria-label="Testimonials">
				<figure class="lp-quote">
					<blockquote>“Finally—filters that match how we actually choose venues.”</blockquote>
					<figcaption>— Alex & Luna 🐕</figcaption>
				</figure>
				<figure class="lp-quote">
					<blockquote>“The amenity confirmations save me so much time. Water bowls = non‑negotiable.”</blockquote>
					<figcaption>— Sam & Mochi 🐾</figcaption>
				</figure>
				<figure class="lp-quote">
					<blockquote>“Perfect on my phone—quick browse, quick decision, happy pup.”</blockquote>
					<figcaption>— Priya & Bean 🐶</figcaption>
				</figure>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="lp-section" id="faq" aria-label="FAQ">
			<div class="lp-section-head">
				<h2 class="lp-h2">Questions, answered 💬</h2>
				<p class="lp-lead">A few MVP details and what’s coming next.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="lp-faq">
				<details class="lp-faq-item">
					<summary>Is this focused on amenities or reviews?</summary>
					<div class="lp-faq-body">Both. Amenities and rules get you to the right list fast, reviews help you decide.</div>
				</details>
				<details class="lp-faq-item">
					<summary>Can I add a venue?</summary>
					<div class="lp-faq-body">Yes—minimal friction: name, location, and at least one amenity/rule indicator.</div>
				</details>
				<details class="lp-faq-item">
					<summary>Will there be a map view?</summary>
					<div class="lp-faq-body">It’s a nice-to-have. The MVP focuses on speed and clarity first.</div>
				</details>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="lp-cta" id="cta" aria-label="Call to action">
			<div class="lp-cta-inner">
				<h2 class="lp-h2">Ready to find your next pet-friendly favorite? 💖</h2>
				<p class="lp-lead">Start browsing, or be the hero who adds the next great spot.</p>
				<div class="lp-hero-actions">
					<a class="lp-btn lp-btn-primary" href="/venues">Browse venues 🔎</a>
					<a class="lp-btn lp-btn-secondary" href="#community">Contribute ➕</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

</main>
